OHSAA Spring Sports Update:
Spring sports for 2020 have officially been canceled in Ohio.
Please reach out to our athletes and especially our seniors to brighten their spring. Please realize Wynford’s coaches, staff and administrators are thinking of you at this time. We would like to thank all our senior athletes for their years of commitment; Wynford Nation is very proud to have had you represent throughout your careers. Life is a journey; great things are ahead for all of you. Enjoy the journey!
